public CarNotificationExtender.Builder setContentId (long contentId)

Sets an id for the content of this notification. If the content id matches an existing notification, the existing notification is updated with the contents of the new notification. If the content id differs from a previous notification posted, this notification is treated as a new notification.

If no content id is specified, the notification is treated as if it has a new content id.

Parameters
contentId long: The content id that represents this notification.
Returns
CarNotificationExtender.Builder This object for method chaining.
